title: Boogie2988 Is Completely Pathetic...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a recent documentary made on Boogie2988 which showcases his rather dark side to a whole bunch of new viewers. Why he thought this was a good idea is beyond me but it prompted me to re-examine this individual and see why he fell from grace. Thanks for watching!
